\c 1
\p 
\v 1 O Anutuu ru sĂ«nĂ«ak yaĂ¶ niiaurĂ¶, ne Yut, Yesu KristoĂ« inĂ«Ă«n ruup, Sems pim nangap, nook pep epwer retĂ«ng Ă« yaningk. Tiarim Pepap Anutuuk lup sant elnieim wĂ«Ă«n Yesu Kristook ngarangk yaalniin ompyaĂ¶ wĂ«.
