\v 20 NemorĂ¶, ar pĂ¶t epĂ«l Ă«Ă«n. Anutuu ngĂ¶n arim kĂ¶n wi kosang yewesa pĂ¶t kĂ¶n wieĂ« arim lupĂ¶t kosang wesak NgĂ«Ă«ngk PulĂ¶Ă¶kĂ« weĂ«re kosangtak piin Ă¶k maim Ă¶n.
\v 21 Anutuuk ar lup sant yaalni pĂ¶taan lup sant pĂ¶t Ă¶nĂ«Ă«taan pim naĂ« Ă¶n. PĂ«l Ă«eĂ« tiarim AkĂ¶p Yesu KristoĂ« yakĂ¶m elniak wĂ«wĂ« kosangĂ«t nimpna pĂ¶ten kor eim Ă¶n.
